OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FCould the Post Office scandal go back
OL,7,Fbefore the Horizon software? ITV News
OL,8,FCorrespondent Chloe Keedy reports
OL,10,FThe stories told in the ITV drama Mr
OL,11,FBates vs The Post Office provoked
OL,12,Fnational outrage. They also turned
OL,13,Ftheir real-life subjects - former
OL,14,Fsubpostmasters and mistresses - into
OL,15,Fhousehold names.
OL,17,FFor months since it aired, revelations
OL,18,Fabout the Post Office have kept
OL,19,Fcoming, as subpostmasters who stayed
OL,20,Fsilent for decades started to share
OL,21,Ftheir own stories.
