OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FBut if you thought the Post Office
OL,7,Fscandal couldn't get any worse, a new
OL,8,FITV documentary might make you think
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,FIt contains allegations that problems
OL,12,Fwith Post Office accounting software
OL,13,Fstarted long before the infamous
OL,14,FHorizon system was introduced,
OL,15,Fclaiming that Capture - its forerunner
OL,16,F- was also faulty.
OL,18,FSteve Marston, 68, believes he was
OL,19,Fwrongly convicted of theft and false
OL,20,Faccounting because of errors caused by
OL,21,FCapture.
