OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FHe received a 12-month suspended
OL,7,Fsentence and was sacked from his
OL,8,Fbranch in Bury, Greater Manchester
OL,9,Fwhen auditors found a shortfall of
OL,10,F#79,000.
OL,12,FSteve lost his income, his savings and
OL,13,Fhis family home. He was forced to
OL,14,Fdeclare himself bankrupt and move into
OL,15,Fa caravan with his wife and two
OL,16,Fchildren.
OL,18,F"We sold our wedding rings, my wife
OL,19,Fsold all of her jewellery. We sold
OL,20,Feverything," Steve told me.
