OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FHe also described being "dropped like
OL,7,Fa stone" by his friends.
OL,9,F"When it came to ... the time to go
OL,10,Ffor sentencing, I was told to try and
OL,11,Fget some references from friends, so I
OL,12,Fwrote to a few and not one of them
OL,13,Fresponded - even my best man."
OL,15,FFor 25 years, Steve believed the
OL,16,Fshortfalls were down to his own
OL,17,F"incompetence".
