OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FIt wasn't until last year when he
OL,7,Fstarted to read about subpostmasters
OL,8,Fwho had had problems with their
OL,9,FHorizon software, that he first
OL,10,Frealised he might not be alone.
OL,12,FSteve is now convinced that Horizon's
OL,13,Fpredecessor was faulty too.
OL,15,FHe showed me a floppy disk which he
OL,16,Fsaid had an old version of Capture on
OL,17,Fit - the same one as he used in his
OL,18,Fpost office.
