OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FWith the help of Rupert Lloyd Thomas,
OL,7,Fa former IT specialist for the Post
OL,8,FOffice who is now working on behalf of
OL,9,Fsubpostmasters, Steve has been running
OL,10,Ftests on old copies of Capture.
OL,12,FHe says seeing the software again has
OL,13,Fbrought back "so many bad memories,"
OL,14,Fbut claims: "We have managed to
OL,15,Freproduce faults, reproduce losses -
OL,16,Fthere isn't a version, from what we
OL,17,Fcan tell, of Capture that hasn't had
OL,18,Fproblems."
