OL,3,CDid the Post Office scandal begin
OL,4,Cbefore the Horizon software?
OL,6,FThe government is now carrying out an
OL,7,Findependent investigation into Capture
OL,8,Fwhich the Post Office says it fully
OL,9,Fsupports. The findings are expected to
OL,10,Fbe published later this month.
OL,12,FSteve hopes it could ultimately lead
OL,13,Fto his conviction finally being
OL,14,Fquashed, which he says would mean
OL,15,F"everything" to him.
OL,17,F"To get my good name back ... It's
OL,18,Fdestroyed us. We're not the people we
OL,19,Fused to be. I used to be outgoing. Now
OL,20,FI get nervous even going into a shop."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
